    "body": "If you want it to work in the meantime, you can use the different subflags for different directories.\r\n\r\nFor the wallet manager it is:\r\n\r\n```\r\nlighthouse account wallet --base-dir test/wallets\r\n```\r\n\r\nSimilarly for the validator account manager it's:\r\n\r\n```\r\nlighthouse account validator --base-dir test/wallets\r\n```\r\n\r\nAnd for the validator client, it's (unfortunately) necessary to set the secrets dir separately:\r\n\r\n```\r\nlighthouse validator_client --datadir test --secrets-dir test/secrets\r\n```",
